      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "In this case server was not set. From the user's perspective it's a very bad way of dealing with inputs. What I'm supposed to do with this output information? (none) That's what output is there for: to inform a user about the internal state. With no output, I have no way to know what is going on, no way of fixing it. And if something is misconfigured the system should exit. Here it just loops on.\n",
